    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43412</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえら、ほんと、ガキの割に強いのな。
訓練とかしてたりするのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow, you two are sure a pair of small powerhouses. What kind of training did you undergo?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>特別、何かやってるって
わけじゃないですけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We don't really do anything special to train ourselves, really...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43608</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱ『なりきり士』の力の
おかげだよな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course it's ‘cause of the Roleplayer powers!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なるほどな。でも力があるからって、
それに頼りきりになるのもどうかと思うぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right, right. But remember, you should never depend on your powers.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうなのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really, now?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43928</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>天から降って湧いた力は、突然、
水が干上がるみたいになくなるかもしれねーしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Imagine having the might to tear apart the land...Suddenly, due to your own powers you realize the ocean has dried up.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44056</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうなった時、慌てないように
元からある力をちゃんときたえといた方がいいぞ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>After that to not make more of a mess wouldn't you want to train hard to control your own strength?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……
よし、明日から超特訓だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're right... Okay till tomorrow I'll train and train and only train!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クル～クル～♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuru kuru!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、調子がいいんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh no, &lt;Dio&gt;'s fired up again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44356</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……なんてな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That he is.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_046_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ずいぶん腕がなまっちまった
オレが言うことじゃねぇけどな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Maybe I shouldn't have told them that after all...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
